CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in New Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, December 1, 1956, pg. A11 reads: " 'Congrats' From Mom - Mildred Ann Briscoe receives a kiss from her mother, Mrs. Lloyd Briscoe, as her godmother, Mrs. Mildred Heywood, and Ernie Tannen, WILY manager, look on. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: "Miss WILY" Mildred Ann Briscoe, receiving a kiss from her mother Mrs. Lloyd Briscoe, as her godmother, Mildred Heywood, and Ernie Tannen look on, standing in Warner's Cinerama Theatre
